Review_Text: Absolutely wonderful - silky and sexy and comfortable

Title: Flattering shirt
Review_Text: This shirt is very flattering to all due to the adjustable front tie. it is the perfect length to wear with leggings and it is sleeveless so it pairs well with any cardigan. love this shirt!!!

Title: Flattering
Review_Text: I love this dress. i usually get an xs but it runs a little snug in bust so i ordered up a size. very flattering and feminine with the usual retailer flair for style.
